	<h1 class="title">「日本語」外国游客是怎么改变了日本人新年的神社参拜？</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/147/small/147.jpg?1418116339" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">陈思吟 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2016-01-09 10:00:32 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/20438/medium/20438.jpg?1452236752" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


